      "title": "Sajith is hospitalized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the leader of the Samagi Jana Balavega, has been admitted to the hospital to receive treatment for a fever. However, it is reported that his condition is not serious and it is a normal viral fever."
